@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1

### 1. Login (Lấy Token)
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "cuog.nc116@gmail.com", 
    "password": "123456"
}

### Lưu token từ phản hồi
@token = {{login.response.body.$.data.token}}

### 2. Xem Giỏ Hàng
GET {{baseUrl}}/carts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Thêm vào Giỏ (Tự tạo cart nếu chưa có)
POST {{baseUrl}}/carts/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "branchId": "CN001",
    "productId": "SP001",
    "quantity": 3
}

### Thêm vào Giỏ (Thêm sản phẩm khác)
POST {{baseUrl}}/carts/add
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "branchId": "CN001",
    "productId": "SP002",
    "quantity": 5
}

### 4. Xóa khỏi Giỏ
POST {{baseUrl}}/carts/remove
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "productId": "SP001"
}

### 5. Thanh Toán (Checkout)
POST {{baseUrl}}/carts/checkout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "branchId": "CN001"
}